{"tid":1142773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"哀鳳落海超崩潰！下秒白色萌物竟叼起來　浮到水面還給她","createTime":"2019-05-07T09:53:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T11:48:17.000Z","uid":32511,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"88dad0605b41dc1cc58df0745abcae64051c721e","tid":1142773,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T09:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reS12sp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreS12sp.jpg&h=e61a8ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0T57dy5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0T57dy5.jpg&h=f3a13e9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小白鯨竟然客串「湖中女神」！挪威有一名女子（Isa）前陣子去海邊遊玩，因一時沒抓穩，手裡的iPhone竟然掉入海中，她當下感到超級絕望，不料這時候水中突然出現一抹白影慢慢浮上來，竟然是一頭小白鯨，而牠嘴巴上還叼著Isa的手機，實在讓人覺得很不可思議！<br />\n<br />\nIsa將她與小白鯨的邂逅放在IG上，從這段影片中可以發現，水底下先是出現一個白色的生物，仔細看嘴巴還叼著東西，浮到水面上這才發現是Isa落水的手機！而當Isa的朋友拿起手機之後，這隻小白鯨還對她們露出友善的笑容，讓兩個人的心都融化了，Isa甚至留言表示「動物比人們還善良」。<br />\n<br />\nIsa事後將該影片授權給「LADbible」臉書粉絲專頁分享，隨即掀起各地網友的熱論，紛紛留言稱「白鯨：請問是你的手機嗎？」、「白鯨：自己的垃圾自己清」、「牠是湖中女神假扮的吧」、「他是怎麼分辨的」、「白鯨應該有3-7歲人類小孩的智力」、「簡直不可思議」。<br />\n<br />\n不過據英國媒體《倫敦標準晚報》報導，有專家指稱這些「聰明」的白鯨可能是俄國海軍訓練的間諜，且挪威漁民日前有發現一隻較大的白鯨，身上繫有「聖彼得堡裝備」等字樣的皮帶，猜測應是固定錄影設備及武器之用。儘管俄國學術單位否認這件事，但該國在前蘇聯時期、1980年代就有訓練海豚等海中哺乳類的計畫。"},{"pid":"a43b069472d56260dfecc50ec58dbef5ea694907","tid":1142773,"uid":208726,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T09:57:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6319c458205cd145841ed39a4dc2ef5535afec5","tid":1142773,"uid":235152,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"只睇標題完全唔知佢想寫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d9269ad8d25691466b782545336dd1511f056f","tid":1142773,"uid":249885,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:22:45.000Z","msg":"標題1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以為係風化新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a139a417363a64bd61781285b7f2a44ba1bc47e1","tid":1142773,"uid":113379,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:32:07.000Z","msg":"台灣記者寫開風化案 自然標題都令人諗風化野<br />\n所以咪話台灣人個腦剩係識1樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d4a229dcae5aa2d832c08a1f41b7f899067fbc","tid":1142773,"uid":26770,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:34:22.000Z","msg":"哀鳳落海仲以為係窮家女做雞......"},{"pid":"1ddbaa57d048aae8f768c12f21de9384f2f872c1","tid":1142773,"uid":13897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a43b069472d56260dfecc50ec58dbef5ea694907","tid":1142773,"uid":208726,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T09:57:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:36:24.000Z","msg":"台灣好鍾意用火星文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16e0435238fe670de226f8727bd6b935796f8c7","tid":1142773,"uid":5196,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:38:22.000Z","msg":"鳳, 落海, 崩潰, 白色, 萌物"},{"pid":"fcdd25647b7755cde0f1a9e10a9feac79e1dcada","tid":1142773,"uid":172507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c16e0435238fe670de226f8727bd6b935796f8c7","tid":1142773,"uid":5196,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:38:22.000Z","msg":"鳳, 落海, 崩潰, 白色, 萌物"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"defc61bcf76c5f2d9710456b7d1044e77f1cbea3","tid":1142773,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:47:17.000Z","msg":"片呢？"},{"pid":"948acac5e20040cb4edf48f694194b11289b179f","tid":1142773,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:47:21.000Z","msg":"哀鳳 iphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as