"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f553fe783de388578814a81a47d2121d0dada2f8","tid":1142773,"uid":55511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:54:36.000Z","msg":"會唔會問係你跌既係金色哀風定銀色哀風"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:56:20.000Z","msg":"都俾哂你啦 反正入水唔用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d22a6c33dc239915114271e8e2a30313fdbff7d","tid":1142773,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d70b64ad8759fc6dae6126aece29fe4cac97c3","tid":1142773,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:05:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n星期六 早上9點 <br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3659a67f1b9ff1059dc486864e2bdc871ca3d9e4","tid":1142773,"uid":130879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:22:43.000Z","msg":"你嗡乜撚野呀台狗？"},{"pid":"eec4a939be3db8cc09d06b8a457f11720566f352","tid":1142773,"uid":128741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d22a6c33dc239915114271e8e2a30313fdbff7d","tid":1142773,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:29:53.000Z","msg":"人扮嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d517c5e9b7492005b1738d46c8d9693dca33d369","tid":1142773,"uid":60545,"lik